tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE call_detail_records (
  record_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  call_duration INT,
  call_quality VARCHAR(255),
  signal_strength INT
)

CREATE TABLE call_detail_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    call_duration INT,
    caller_number VARCHAR(10),
    receiver_number VARCHAR(10),
    quality_of_service DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE network_optimization (
    optimization_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    optimization_type VARCHAR(50),
    optimization_description TEXT,
    date_created DATE,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE call_detail_records (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    caller_number VARCHAR,
    receiver_number VARCHAR,
    call_duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE network_performance (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    download_speed INT,
    upload_speed INT,
    latency INT
);
